# Sales Data Analysis

## Project Overview

This project analyzes retail sales data using SQL and Python.

## Tools Used

- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- SQL
- Excel

## Project Files

- sales_data.csv
- sales_queries.sql
- sales_analysis.py

## Key Insights

- Total Sales
- Total Profit
- Sales by Category
- Sales by City
- Top Products

## Skills Demonstrated

- Data Cleaning
- SQL
- Python
- Data Visualization
- Business Analysis
